1:31:10.291 --> 1:31:13.500
I mean, for God's sake,
we took a fucking picture of it!

1:31:13.583 --> 1:31:15.291
What other proof do we need?

1:31:15.791 --> 1:31:18.375
And if we can't all agree
at the bare minimum

1:31:18.458 --> 1:31:22.875
that a giant comet
the size of Mount Everest

1:31:22.958 --> 1:31:29.041
hurtling its way towards planet Earth
is not a fucking good thing,

1:31:29.833 --> 1:31:32.125
then what the hell happened to us?

1:31:33.000 --> 1:31:37.333
I mean, my God, how do--
How do we even talk to each other?

1:31:37.416 --> 1:31:41.208
What've we… What've we done to ourselves?
How do we fix it?

1:31:41.291 --> 1:31:44.791
We should have deflected this comet
when we had the fucking chance,

1:31:44.875 --> 1:31:48.083
but we didn't do it.
I don't know why we didn't do it.

1:31:48.166 --> 1:31:51.958
And now they're
actually firing scientists like me

1:31:52.041 --> 1:31:54.666
for speaking out, for opposing them.

1:31:55.416 --> 1:31:57.875
And I'm sure many of the people out there

1:31:57.958 --> 1:31:59.958
aren't even
gonna listen to what I just said

1:32:00.041 --> 1:32:02.833
'cause they have
their own political ideology,

1:32:03.500 --> 1:32:05.916
but I… assure you,

1:32:06.583 --> 1:32:08.583
I am not on one side or the other.

1:32:08.666 --> 1:32:10.916
I'm just telling you the fucking truth.

1:32:11.000 --> 1:32:12.625
This would be a good time to establish

1:32:12.708 --> 1:32:15.250
that Isherwell and the president
have both said

1:32:15.333 --> 1:32:16.958
that there's benefits to be--

1:32:17.041 --> 1:32:21.750
Right, well, the president
of the United States is fucking lying!

1:32:23.125 --> 1:32:24.708
Look, I'm just like all of you.

1:32:24.791 --> 1:32:29.833
I hope to God, I hope to God that
this president knows what she's doing.

1:32:29.916 --> 1:32:33.750
I hope she's got us all taken care of,
but the truth is,

1:32:33.833 --> 1:32:36.875
I think this whole administration

1:32:36.958 --> 1:32:41.500
has completely lost their fucking mind!

1:32:41.583 --> 1:32:45.125
And I think we're all gonna die!

1:32:45.833 --> 1:32:47.625
[breathing heavily]

1:32:49.291 --> 1:32:51.125
[softly] Look, I just wanna go home.

1:32:51.791 --> 1:32:54.125
[sighs] I just wanna go home.

1:32:54.208 --> 1:32:56.125
I just wanna go home more than anything.

1:32:56.208 --> 1:32:58.583
[breathing heavily]

1:33:00.875 --> 1:33:02.583
But if there is one thing,

1:33:03.208 --> 1:33:05.291
one thing that I pray…

1:33:05.375 --> 1:33:09.833
that I pray that all of you hear
from what I have just said,

1:33:10.625 --> 1:33:13.583
is that all of us, all of us…

1:33:15.958 --> 1:33:17.291
[car door opens]

1:33:18.750 --> 1:33:19.750
[sighs]

1:33:22.083 --> 1:33:23.625
Why'd you do that?

1:33:24.750 --> 1:33:28.250
I really liked you
and I despise most people.

1:33:29.791 --> 1:33:33.000
[Mindy] You know, I…
I really thought I loved you.

1:33:35.791 --> 1:33:36.958
Really?

1:33:37.875 --> 1:33:38.750
Wow.

1:33:40.375 --> 1:33:41.833
[sighs] That's wild.

1:33:43.000 --> 1:33:44.625
-Yeah.
-[car door opens]

1:33:44.708 --> 1:33:47.416
[man] Ma'am, you need to go.
We gotta get this man off the grid.

1:33:49.500 --> 1:33:50.708
[Mindy] You still there?

1:33:53.750 --> 1:33:54.791
No.

1:33:57.291 --> 1:34:01.041
[Kate] Well, maybe he just gets off
on the power, you know,

1:34:01.125 --> 1:34:02.791
like any kind of power.

1:34:02.875 --> 1:34:07.750
