gonna find out that the snacks were free.

1:34:07.833 --> 1:34:09.291
-Right.
-You know what I mean?

1:34:09.375 --> 1:34:11.833
-Yeah.
-So it was just like a power play.

1:34:12.541 --> 1:34:13.625
Yeah, guys are weird.

1:34:16.250 --> 1:34:20.000
I'm starting to think that all this
"end of the world" stuff is bullshit.

1:34:21.625 --> 1:34:22.833
It's not.

1:34:22.916 --> 1:34:26.833
It's definitely happening. I've seen it.

1:34:27.416 --> 1:34:31.041
I feel like if God wanted to destroy
the Earth, He would destroy the Earth.

1:34:33.333 --> 1:34:34.583
You believe in God?

1:34:36.541 --> 1:34:39.166
Yeah, I mean,
my parents raised me Evangelical,

1:34:39.250 --> 1:34:41.583
and I hate them,
but I found my own way to it.

1:34:41.666 --> 1:34:42.916
My own relationship.

1:34:44.333 --> 1:34:45.458
[Kate] Hmm.

1:34:46.416 --> 1:34:48.708
I'd appreciate it
if you didn't advertise it, though.

1:34:52.041 --> 1:34:55.166
I won't tell anybody. [chuckles]
I think it's kind of sweet.

1:34:58.750 --> 1:35:01.333
-Wanna make out?
-Yeah, why not?

1:35:02.458 --> 1:35:05.458
