With the boys ♪

1:35:31.666 --> 1:35:33.416
♪ Honky tonks and pretty… ♪

1:35:42.708 --> 1:35:44.833
-Oh, my God, that's it.
-What? What?

1:35:44.916 --> 1:35:47.166
-That's the comet.
-What? Where?

1:35:47.708 --> 1:35:48.750
[gasps]

1:35:48.833 --> 1:35:51.916
-[Yule] Where? Uh-huh.
-Well, that's the Big Dipper.

1:35:52.000 --> 1:35:54.916
-That's Venus. That's the North Star.
-Uh-huh.

1:35:55.500 --> 1:35:57.958
-Well, what is that?
-Oh, shit.

1:35:58.041 --> 1:35:59.083
[Kate chuckles]

1:35:59.166 --> 1:36:05.875
♪ Sometimes I feel like Jesse James
Still trying to make a name ♪

1:36:06.458 --> 1:36:07.708
What the hell?

1:36:07.791 --> 1:36:10.416
♪ Knowing nothing's gonna change
What I am ♪

1:36:10.500 --> 1:36:11.500
What?

1:36:13.750 --> 1:36:14.583
Come on.

1:36:14.666 --> 1:36:16.791
[horns honking]

1:36:22.208 --> 1:36:23.208
There it is.

1:36:23.291 --> 1:36:24.458
[horns honking]

1:36:25.958 --> 1:36:27.125
There you are.

1:36:30.166 --> 1:36:31.166
There you are.

1:36:32.083 --> 1:36:34.250
Is anyone else seeing this? That's it.

1:36:35.041 --> 1:36:38.833
That's it. That's the comet.
Look! It's right there.

1:36:38.916 --> 1:36:39.791
[man shouting]

1:36:39.875 --> 1:36:42.875
[uneasy music playing]

1:37:14.833 --> 1:37:16.250
-[gasps]
-[cell phone vibrating]

1:37:16.333 --> 1:37:19.291
-That's, you know, kinda scary.
-Oh! Exactly.

1:37:23.791 --> 1:37:25.625
-Dr. Mindy.
-[Mindy] Kate.

1:37:25.708 --> 1:37:27.875
Doc, you can see it.

1:37:27.958 --> 1:37:32.166
I… I'm looking at it right now too.
It's unbelievable. It's…

1:37:32.666 --> 1:37:36.250
It's horrific and it's…
And it's beautiful at the same time.

1:37:36.333 --> 1:37:38.041
-Oh, my God.
-[laughing]

1:37:43.208 --> 1:37:45.125
We've been trying to tell you.

1:37:45.750 --> 1:37:49.041
We tried to tell you this whole time.
It's right there. It's…

1:37:49.875 --> 1:37:51.458
It's right there, Kate.

1:37:51.541 --> 1:37:52.625
[horns honking]

1:37:54.291 --> 1:37:55.375
[Kate] Where are you?

1:37:55.458 --> 1:37:56.875
I'm in Lansing, Michigan

1:37:56.958 --> 1:38:00.125
trying to fix things with June,
but she won't talk to me.

1:38:00.208 --> 1:38:02.083
-Where are you?
-[Yule] What the fuck?

1:38:03.041 --> 1:38:04.166
[Kate] I…

1:38:04.250 --> 1:38:06.291
[Mindy] I'm gonna come find you, okay?

1:38:07.375 --> 1:38:10.708
Well, I'm in Illinois.
I could be ready by tomorrow.

1:38:12.083 --> 1:38:13.375
-Dearest Father…
-Yeah, I'm--

1:38:13.458 --> 1:38:16.000
…as a sinner I come to You
for Your grace and guidance…

1:38:16.083 --> 1:38:18.125
[Mindy] They're finally seeing it.

1:38:18.708 --> 1:38:20.250
They're finally seeing it.

1:38:20.333 --> 1:38:22.166
[uneasy music continues playing]

1:38:26.083 --> 1:38:27.583
There it is!

1:38:34.708 --> 1:38:35.916
[grunting]

1:38:38.333 --> 1:38:39.583
[cooing]

1:38:39.666 --> 1:38:41.541
[bell dinging]

1:38:41.625 --> 1:38:45.208
Go outside into your yard,
onto a roof, onto your sidewalk,

1:38:45.291 --> 1:38:46.708
and just look up into the sky.

1:38:46.791 --> 1:38:50.125
The star's gonna appear fuzzy.
It's got a long streak coming off of it.

1:38:50.208 --> 1:38:51.708
That's the comet's tail.

1:38:51.791 --> 1:38:53.375
It's real and it's coming.

1:38:53.458 --> 1:38:56.041
If anyone tells you any different,
they're full of shit.

1:38:56.125 --> 1:38:57.625
Just look up into the sky.

1:38:57.708 --> 1:38:59.166
It's a fucking fact.

1:38:59.250 --> 1:39:00.708
-We have proof.
-Just look up.

1:39:00.791 --> 1:39:04.416
Guys, please just look up, okay?
Screw the manatees and just look up.

1:39:04.500 --> 1:39:05.458
[both] Just look up.

1:39:05.541 --> 1:39:07.625
-[all] Just look up!
-Just look up! Just look up!

1:39:07.708 --> 1:39:08.708
Just look up!

1:39:08.791 --> 1:39:13.083
Dr. Mindy, the president's
plan to save Earth

1:39:13.166 --> 1:39:18.125
and make it so we can all have a home
is going to work, right?

1:39:18.208 --> 1:39:22.250
Every single man, woman and child
on this planet is going to die.

1:39:22.333 --> 1:39:25.541
-I don't like him. He makes me sad.
-I'm sorry about that.

1:39:25.625 --> 1:39:27.625
