-Kids, listen.

1:39:27.708 --> 1:39:30.875
You tell your parents
that President Orlean and Isherwell

1:39:30.958 --> 1:39:32.625
are sociopaths and fascists!

1:39:32.708 --> 1:39:34.583
[cheers and applause]

1:39:39.791 --> 1:39:42.708
And do you know why
they want you to look up?

1:39:43.666 --> 1:39:45.416
Do you know why?

1:39:45.500 --> 1:39:48.041
'Cause they want you to be afraid.

1:39:48.125 --> 1:39:49.416
[audience cheering]

1:39:49.500 --> 1:39:51.958
They want you to look up

1:39:52.041 --> 1:39:54.708
because they are
looking down their noses at you.

1:39:56.041 --> 1:39:57.916
They think they're better than you.

1:39:58.000 --> 1:40:00.500
-[hip-hop tune plays]
-[chanting] Don't look up!

1:40:00.583 --> 1:40:02.833
They wanna rob you of your freedom,
and that's a fact!

1:40:02.916 --> 1:40:05.000
[chanting] Don't look up!

1:40:05.083 --> 1:40:06.833
The US president, Orlean…

1:40:06.916 --> 1:40:09.250
-[crowd clamoring]
-[man yelling] Just look up!

1:40:09.333 --> 1:40:12.625
…has not included India
or any other nation in the world

1:40:12.708 --> 1:40:14.041
to be a part of this mission.

1:40:14.750 --> 1:40:17.375
This dude is a known pornographer
named Kip…

1:40:17.458 --> 1:40:18.708
Don't listen to that dumbfuck.

1:40:18.791 --> 1:40:24.791
The United Nations have been
considering its own deflective mission.

1:40:24.875 --> 1:40:27.125
-[laughing]
-Just look up, for fuck's sake!

1:40:27.208 --> 1:40:30.958
[woman] Now I know a lot of Hollywood
is supporting the Just Look Up movement,

1:40:31.041 --> 1:40:32.875
but I haven't seen a pin like that.

1:40:32.958 --> 1:40:37.708
Yeah, this pin points both up and down.

1:40:38.291 --> 1:40:42.916
Because I think, as a country,
we need to stop arguing

1:40:43.000 --> 1:40:45.500
and virtue signaling. Just get along.

1:40:46.125 --> 1:40:48.500
-[woman] That is so refreshing.
-Hmm.

1:40:48.583 --> 1:40:51.208
[woman] I think
we're all tired of the politics.

1:40:51.291 --> 1:40:53.458
Yeah, yeah. Well…

1:40:54.458 --> 1:40:56.083
That's why we made Total Devastation.

1:40:56.166 --> 1:40:58.291
It's for everyone. You know?
It's a popcorn movie.

1:40:58.375 --> 1:41:02.083
You keep your eye on the road ahead,
you put your head down.

1:41:02.166 --> 1:41:04.583
And you put
one foot in front of the other,

1:41:04.666 --> 1:41:05.708
step by step.

1:41:05.791 --> 1:41:06.916
[people cheering]

1:41:07.000 --> 1:41:08.083
[Orlean] Day by day.

1:41:08.166 --> 1:41:11.375
-[people chanting] Don't look up!
-Don't!

1:41:11.458 --> 1:41:13.458
[captivating music playing]

1:41:17.458 --> 1:41:20.500
So we wanna say something loud and clear.

1:41:20.583 --> 1:41:24.208
There is no safe way
to bring this comet back to Earth

1:41:24.291 --> 1:41:27.000
and exploit it for profit.
It cannot be done!

1:41:27.583 --> 1:41:31.458
Nations of the world,
defy Orlean and BASH!

1:41:31.541 --> 1:41:36.083
Launch your own nuclear deflection mission
now and save this planet!

1:41:36.166 --> 1:41:37.458
[breathing heavily]

1:41:37.541 --> 1:41:43.375
And now, uh, there's Riley Bina
with her special guest.

1:41:43.458 --> 1:41:45.708
-[people cheering]
-I forgot the name. Thank you.

1:41:47.416 --> 1:41:50.666
["Just Look Up" playing]

1:41:50.750 --> 1:41:53.750
[Riley vocalizing]

1:42:02.125 --> 1:42:08.416
♪ We knew no bounds
Fell at the speed of sound ♪

1:42:08.500 --> 1:42:14.416
♪ Riding against all odds but soon
Against ourselves ♪

1:42:16.375 --> 1:42:20.333
♪ You haunted every memory ♪

1:42:20.416 --> 1:42:24.125
♪ With no goodbyes out there for me ♪

1:42:24.208 --> 1:42:30.208
♪ Your pride put out the fire
