1:42:31.250 --> 1:42:34.750
♪ Then just one look is all it takes ♪

1:42:34.833 --> 1:42:40.458
♪ I feel your eyes
They're locked on every part of me ♪

1:42:40.541 --> 1:42:45.291
♪ And then my dumb heart says ♪

1:42:45.375 --> 1:42:49.458
♪ Just look up ♪

1:42:49.541 --> 1:42:53.166
