They're there…

1:43:46.833 --> 1:43:49.333
♪ Know I let you down
A nigga can't deny it ♪

1:43:50.541 --> 1:43:53.166
♪ And there's so much that we're losin'
Yes, that matters ♪

1:43:53.250 --> 1:43:56.541
♪ I've been dealin' with madness
Wasn't the man you needed ♪

1:43:57.250 --> 1:44:00.500
♪ You dealin' with sadness
Truthfully, it's all on me… ♪

1:44:01.291 --> 1:44:04.083
-[Oglethorpe] Divest from BASH when?
-[people] Divest now!

1:44:04.166 --> 1:44:05.833
Divest from BASH when?

1:44:07.791 --> 1:44:08.875
♪ Time is oh so precious… ♪

1:44:08.958 --> 1:44:10.541
We will not be quiet!

1:44:11.583 --> 1:44:14.958
♪ Take my hand, baby
I'll never leave you, Riley ♪

1:44:15.041 --> 1:44:19.375
♪ Though what he's really trying to say ♪

1:44:19.458 --> 1:44:23.083
♪ Is get your head out of your ass ♪

1:44:23.166 --> 1:44:29.916
♪ Listen to the goddamn
Qualified scientists ♪

1:44:30.000 --> 1:44:33.416
♪ We really fucked it up
Fucked it up this time ♪

1:44:33.500 --> 1:44:37.333
♪ It's so close
I can feel the heat big-time ♪

1:44:37.416 --> 1:44:41.000
♪ And you can act
Like everything is all right ♪

1:44:41.083 --> 1:44:44.791
♪ But this is probably
Happening in real time ♪

1:44:44.875 --> 1:44:47.791
♪ Celebrate or cry or pray ♪

1:44:47.875 --> 1:44:53.166
♪ Whatever it takes
To get you through the mess that we made ♪

1:44:53.250 --> 1:44:58.208
♪ 'Cause tomorrow may never come ♪

1:44:58.291 --> 1:45:02.625
♪ Just look up ♪

1:45:02.708 --> 1:45:06.291
♪ Turn off the shitbox news ♪

1:45:06.375 --> 1:45:09.333
♪ 'Cause you're about to die soon
Everybody ♪

1:45:09.416 --> 1:45:13.208
[vocalizing]

1:45:13.291 --> 1:45:15.000
♪ Look up… ♪

1:45:15.083 --> 1:45:16.541
[cell phone ringing]

1:45:18.500 --> 1:45:19.583
[Oglethorpe] Oh.

1:45:20.541 --> 1:45:23.833
Hey, good afternoon, Adam.
What do I owe the pleasure of this call?

1:45:30.041 --> 1:45:31.041
What time?

1:45:33.833 --> 1:45:35.416
[explosion]

1:45:38.791 --> 1:45:41.708
Well, uh… Well, thank you for calling.

1:45:41.791 --> 1:45:42.708
Um…

1:45:44.125 --> 1:45:45.125
Yeah.

1:45:56.125 --> 1:45:58.583
[indistinct conversation]

1:46:01.583 --> 1:46:02.541
What?

1:46:05.958 --> 1:46:06.958
What?

1:46:09.916 --> 1:46:14.708
Orlean and BASH
cut Russia, India, and China

1:46:15.958 --> 1:46:17.375
out of the rights for the minerals.

