1:47:14.083 --> 1:47:15.083
[Mindy] Fuck!

1:47:15.166 --> 1:47:17.333
["Just Like Paradise" playing on speakers]

1:47:21.833 --> 1:47:23.250
[people cheering]

1:47:27.291 --> 1:47:30.083
These Just Look Uppers

